text: Aymen Benabderrahmane (; born 30 August 1966) is an Algerian politician who is serving as Prime Minister of Algeria from 30 June 2021 until 11 November 2023 and Minister of Finance from 23 June 2020 until 17 February 2022. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Prime ministers of Algeria
title: Aymen Benabderrahmane
